         <abstract id="aspace_d704ab5384c249c35933c1a2d895ea17">Durham's Folio Club was founded by
            Duke University faculty wives and other Duke-affiliated women in 1927. This collection
            includes the records of the Folio Club, including meeting minutes, programs,
            correspondence, and clippings related to the activities of the club and its
            members.</abstract>
